# Files prettier can't reliably parse — skip them in `--check` and `--write`.

# JSONC (JSON with // comments) — prettier-3 parses as strict JSON.
.devcontainer/devcontainer.json
**/tsconfig*.json

# TOML — prettier-3 has no built-in TOML parser (would also be caught by
# our lint-staged glob, but defense in depth).
**/*.toml

# Build / cache outputs
**/dist/**
**/build/**
**/coverage/**
**/node_modules/**
**/.vite/**
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
